                     <div class="about-modal-content">
                       <h2 class="about-heading">About Moritz</h2>
                       <p class="text-color-sec">
                         As the son of an industrial designer, it didn’t take me long to
                         fall in love with design and technology. For as long as I can
                         think, I’ve been behind screens, tearing apart designs &
                         websites to discover the craft behind them. This quickly led to
                         working as a freelance web designer and
                         <span class="about-modal-ear-content"
                           >developer next to school and evolved into a true passion.
                           Fast forward a few years, and I stumbled across Webflow – I
                           was immediately drawn in and understood its full potential. I
                           went all in.</span
                         ><br />
                         <br />For the past 5 years, I’ve been working full-time as an
                         independent Webflow developer with clients I could only dream of
                         a while ago. I deeply care about honesty and transparency, it’s
                         at the center of everything I do. My passion is building
                         <span class="about-modal-bottom-content"
                           >remarkable things with companies and teams who share the same
                           care and commitment as I do.</span
                         >
                       </p>
